    "title": "Junior Revenue Manager at MakeMyTrip Hotels Advisory Limited",
    "description": "Grow your career with MakeMyTrip Hotels Advisory Limited! We are hiring a Revenue Manager for our Bhubaneswar team. Be part of a workplace that celebrates innovation, diversity, and performance.\n\nAbout MakeMyTrip Hotels Advisory Limited:\nMakeMyTrip Hotels Advisory Limited is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Plan and execute banquets, events, and MICE functions\n• Assist in menu planning, costing, and food festival coordination\n• Manage procurement of hotel supplies and control operating costs\n• Handle guest complaints and resolve issues promptly\n• Develop and maintain relationships with corporate clients\n• Conduct regular guest satisfaction surveys and implement improvements\n• Ensure compliance with FSSAI, health, and safety regulations\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Post Graduate Diploma in relevant field\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Housekeeping Standards\n• Proficiency in Hotel Management\n• Proficiency in Sommelier Skills\n• Proficiency in GDS Systems\n• Proficiency in Revenue Management\n• Proficiency in Crisis Management\n• Proficiency in Tour Planning\n• Proficiency in Event Management\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Learning & development budget\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Bhubaneswar, Odisha, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with MakeMyTrip Hotels Advisory Limited!",
